short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Augment your foodie experience with this plugin dedicated to Deliveroo!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Our goal with JoeyroopPlus is to provide an augmented experience to all foodies who love discovering new places on Deliveroo's website. 

This first version introduces Yelp ratings that can click out to Yelp restaurant pages. Next updates will introduce food images and other sources of data to help you pick the right meal for the right occasion.

Feedback and Ideas are welcome on the Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/joeyrooplus

Update:
- May 1st 2017 : Added support for deliveroo.de.
